### v1.0 — Foundation ✅ (Current)
- [x] Secret scanner (200+ patterns)
- [x] Dependency vulnerability check (npm, PyPI, cargo, rubygems)
- [x] System security audit (Linux, macOS, Windows)
- [x] Git history scanning
- [x] Report export (PDF, HTML, JSON)
- [x] English & Arabic language support

### v1.5 — Integration & Expansion
- [ ] GitHub Actions marketplace action
- [ ] Pre-commit hook integration
- [ ] VS Code extension
- [ ] Docker container scan
- [ ] Kubernetes configuration audit
- [ ] 10+ additional languages

### v2.0 — Intelligence
- [ ] AI-powered remediation suggestions
- [ ] Custom rule engine (write your own patterns)
- [ ] Team dashboard (local, self-hosted)
- [ ] Historical trend tracking
- [ ] Compliance templates (GDPR, SOC 2, ISO 27001, PCI DSS)

### v2.5 — Community & Ecosystem
- [ ] Community-contributed security checks database
- [ ] Plugin system for third-party integrations
- [ ] Mobile companion app (iOS/Android)

